OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fscattered showers, these most frequent
OL,7,Facross the west. Drier across eastern
OL,8,FAberdeenshire. Fresh occasionally
OL,9,Fstrong westerly winds, easing this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading from
OL,14,Fthe southwest. Rain patchy across the
OL,15,Feast and along the north coast. Strong
OL,16,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
